### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### 图书搜索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/search?keyword=人工智能&tag=入门&page=0&size=10

### 书城分区
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/store?section=featured&userId=10086&page=0&size=8

### 图书详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### 本地 TXT/MD/EPUB 入库
POST http://localhost:8080/api/import/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "file_name": "考研英语写作笔记.txt",
  "source_type": "local_txt",
  "content": "第一章 写作素材\n\n考研英语写作需要主题素材、句式和限时输出训练。",
  "tags": "本地导入,考研,英语",
  "target_reader": "准备考研英语写作训练的学生"
}

### 用户画像
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile?userId=10086

### 保存画像
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "name": "测试同学",
  "major": "计算机科学",
  "grade": "大二",
  "interests": "人工智能,算法,英语备考",
  "goal": "课程拓展与竞赛入门",
  "budget": 80,
  "channels": "library,jd,dangdang,second_hand"
}

### AI 推荐
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ai/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "query": "我想看适合零基础的人工智能入门书"
}

### AI 伴读
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "book_id": 1,
  "question": "这本书里智能体是什么意思？"
}

### 保存笔记
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "book_id": 1,
  "content": "智能体是在环境中感知并行动的系统。",
  "type": "ai_answer"
}

### 创建计划
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "book_id": 1,
  "target_days": 14
}

### 电商/馆藏聚合
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commerce/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "book_id": 1,
  "isbn": "9787111649312",
  "channels": ["library", "jd", "dangdang", "second_hand"]
}

### 购买/借阅确认
POST http://localhost:8080/api/purchase/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 10086,
  "book_id": 1,
  "platform": "library",
  "action": "reserve",
  "amount": 0,
  "confirmed": true
}
